UID:NR-v9H8tF9arueNQ0OF5r
SUMMARY:West Coast Grill & BBQ Sauces Class
DTSTAMP:20260314T153648Z
DTSTART:20260314T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:A delicious walk through the four styles of American barbecue s
	auces from Kansas City \, Memphis \, Texas\, and North Carolina . Sweet & 
	sour too spicy\, too tangy\, too sweet\, each sauce represents the region\
	, along with the traditional meats from each locale. To go with the cookin
	g class is an introduction to Chef Traci’s West Coast Grill . This 90-minu
	te class is the perfect way to hone your sauce skills\, learn new sauces\,
	 and spice up your grilling techniques. Please note: pork and beef are the
	 primary proteins for this class. This is the perfect holiday gift for you
	r favorite grill master! Buy Tickets\n\nhttps://www.pikeplacemarket.org/ev
	ents-calendar/west-coast-grill-bbq-sauces-class-530pm/?occurrence=2026-03-
